page.title: 05MY HOME IN PARTNEY
page.content: I live in a big house with a big garden and lots of country side around me.There are 5 fields 5 gardens and 1 barn. I love my house very much. I would not sell it for anything. In side the house there are 7 bedrooms. I have a bedroom of my own. Mum is going to put some shelves in it and she has put a desk in it already. It also has a bed to sleep in like most people have. I keep my toys in it. We have 3 bathrooms 2 upstairs 1 downstairs. We have a back door and a front door. 3 kitchens 1 drawing room.We have a playroom too.Our house is old it is 283 years old.
